-lrb- cnn -rrb- roseanne barr revealed earlier this week that she is going blind .
in an interview with the daily beast , the 62-year-old comic talked about her struggle with macular degeneration and glaucoma -- two eye diseases that get progressively worse over time and can steal vision .
macular degeneration is a breakdown of the part of the retina that allows us to see fine details in the center of vision ; while glaucoma damages the nerve that connects the retina to the brain , and is often caused by fluid build-up and pressure in the eyes .
-lrb- barr said in the interview that she helps relieve the pressure by using marijuana , which is known to temporarily lower pressure inside the eye .
